casebody.data:
Marks, Respondent, v. Metropolitan Life Ins. Co., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 10, 1890.) Appeal from first district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Arnoux, Ritch & Woodford, for appellant. M. L. Erlanger, for respondent.

No opinion. Motion that the appeal be withdrawn without costs to either party granted.
